 content="""
I have updated [[design/external_special_remote_protocol/export_and_import_appendix]]
to document this new interface. I decided to not try to support a combined
exporttree=yes and importtree=yes for external special remotes because
noone has ever stepped forward to implement an external special remote that
can safely do that. I know it will be much easier and safer to implement
importtree only external special remotes.

The external special remote interface for this still needs to be
implemented.
